And who would want her not to be able to compete?

00:04:51.941 --> 00:04:57.911
Well, all eyes turned to who would stand to benefit with Kerrigan out of the picture.

00:04:59.291 --> 00:05:03.191
The obvious candidate was her main rival, Tonya Harding,

